  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The deep speaks in vowels. Wreck body mode with feedback 0.78 creates spectral complexity. Filter resonance at 0.8 with cutoff at 320 Hz produces a strong formant peak. LFO1 modulates the cutoff by 50 Hz at 0.1 Hz — the formant slowly shifts between 'oo' and 'oh' vowels. The mod wheel darkens the formant further toward 'uh'. Three vowels from one filter, no formant synthesis required.",
  "tags": [
    "bass",
    "formant",
    "vowel",
    "speaking",
    "spectral",
    "guru-bin",
    "transcendental"
  ],
